data.description: You'll love the space and value in this brick ranch home in Des Plaines.  This home features a traditional layout, a large basement, an attached garage.  This property is located just 2-3 blocks from Downtown Des Plaines with many amenities such as restaurants, shopping and the Metra station.  This is a Fannie Mae HomePath property.
